<section id="ddb-importer-muncher-sources" class="tab ddb-muncher {{ tab.cssClass }} {{#if tab.active}} active{{/if}}" data-tab="{{ tab.id }}" data-group="{{ tab.group }}">

    <fieldset>
    <legend>Choose Ingredients (Sourcebooks)</legend>
    <p>If any books are selected here DDB Importer will filter content that is <i>only</i> in that book.
Please note that sometimes DDB marks a book as from it's first source only, e.g. the SRD/Basic rules for some monsters.
These interact with the Exclusion settings below.
It is recommended you use Exclusion rules rather than filtering explicitly by source book
This will ensure you get all the spells, items and monsters you are expecting.
</p>
    {{#each sourceConfig}}
    <div class="form-group munching-source-config">
      <label>{{ this.label }}</label>
      <div class="form-fields">
        <dnd5e-checkbox name="{{this.name}}" id="munching-source-policy-{{this.name}}" {{#if this.isChecked}}checked{{/if}}
        data-section="{{this.name}}" {{#if this.enabled}}enabled{{else}}disabled{{/if}}></dnd5e-checkbox>
      </div>
      <p class="hint">{{{this.hint}}}</p>
    </div>
    {{/each}}
    <div id="munch-source-div" {{#if enableSources}}{{else}}class="ddbimporter-hidden"{{/if}}>
      <multi-select id="muncher-source-select" name="muncher-source-select">
        {{#each selectedSources}}
        <option value="{{this.id}}" {{this.selected}}> {{this.label}}</option>
        {{/each}}
      </multi-select>
    </div>
    </fieldset>
    <fieldset>
    <legend>Excluded Flavour Profiles (Categories)</legend>
    <p>By default DDB Importer <strong>excludes</strong> third party categories from being imported.</p>
    <p>The following categories will be excluded. Please adjust to taste.</p>
    <p>Categories are used on D&D Beyond to filter content.
These are groups of books.
The 2024 PHB, MM and DMG are considered "Core Rules".
Expanded content are books like XGtE.
Legacy/non-core are books that were replaced in the 2014 ruleset lifecycle like Mordenkainenâ€™s Tome of Foes.</p>
    <div class="form-fields" id="munch-excluded-config">
      <multi-select id="muncher-excluded-source-categories" name="muncher-excluded-source-categories">
        {{#each excludedCategories}}
        <option value="{{this.id}}" {{this.selected}}> {{this.label}}</option>
        {{/each}}
      </multi-select>
    </div>
    </fieldset>

</section>
